snippet.title: GoD Factory: Wingmen Reveal Trailer (Pre-alpha)
snippet.description:
Greenlight : http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=134884522
Kickstarter : http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ninedots/god-factory-wingmen

Music: Horizon by Geoplex, go check out his facebook page: www.facebook.com/Geoplex

GoD Factory: Wingmen is a 4v4 competitive space combat sim in which you assemble your ships part by part. The goal is to destroy the enemy carrier ship while protecting your own. For more information on the game, visit our development blog on www.ninedotsstudio.com.
